Package: calipeRmatching
Type: Package
Title: Caliper Matching Estimator for Average Treatment Effects
Version: 1.0
Author: Mate Kormos
Maintainer: Mate Kormos <mate.kormos@runbox.com>
Description: Caliper matching estimator of the Average Treatment Effect and the Average Treatment Effect on the Treated of a binary treatment. 
        A treated and a control unit are matched if their propensity scores (either known or estimated parametric) are within a specified distance called the caliper. See [KPV23] <arXiv:2304.08373> for details.
URL: https://arxiv.org/abs/2304.08373, https://github.com/kmmate/calipeRmatching, https://github.com/kmmate/caliper_matching
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.11)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Encoding: UTF-8
